1387
01:53:11,703 --> 01:53:17,588
"The face was supposed to
reflect a man's heart"

1388
01:53:17,843 --> 01:53:24,467
"I mistook every expression
that his face registered"

1389
01:53:24,547 --> 01:53:25,998
"What was he in reality"

1390
01:53:26,078 --> 01:53:30,644
"And what did I take him for"

1391
01:53:51,695 --> 01:53:58,048
"I lost everything and was
still heart-broken"

1392
01:54:01,611 --> 01:54:07,373
"I lost everything and was
still heart-broken"

1393
01:54:07,752 --> 01:54:14,216
"And I took the pain
as a gift of love"

1394
01:54:14,296 --> 01:54:16,520
"What was he in reality"

1395
01:54:16,600 --> 01:54:20,465
"And what did I take him for"

1396
01:54:20,931 --> 01:54:27,406
"How could I revere
