1397
01:54:27,486 --> 01:54:29,530
"What was he in reality"

1398
01:54:29,610 --> 01:54:33,750
"And what did I take him for"

1399
01:54:34,005 --> 01:54:36,231
"What was he in reality"

1400
01:54:36,311 --> 01:54:40,814
"And what did I take him for"

1401
01:54:43,163 --> 01:54:44,658
Get up, brother-in-law.

1402
01:54:44,744 --> 01:54:48,467
Let me rest. My son has
laid me out flat!

1403
01:54:48,818 --> 01:54:51,334
Your wife wants to touch your feet,
today being the Karva Chauth day.

1404
01:54:51,414 --> 01:54:52,783
Very well.

1405
01:54:53,247 --> 01:54:55,716
This is the only day I get
her to touch my feet!

1406
01:54:56,235 --> 01:54:57,906
Bless you with
all the happiness!

1407
01:54:59,208 --> 01:55:01,434
My son was the rose who
has now become a thorn.

1408
01:55:02,727 --> 01:55:04,416
Today is the day of the
Karva Chauth fast.

1409
01:55:04,891 --> 01:55:08,736
Had Madhuri been here,
we've have been together...

1410
01:55:10,320 --> 01:55:12,962
Anyway... we're going
to the temple.

1411
01:55:13,042 --> 01:55:17,525
Sure. And pray that
you're together next year.

1412
01:55:19,328 --> 01:55:21,783
You haven't touched my
feet, Saraswati!

1413
01:55:22,003 --> 01:55:24,396
Today's not Holi!
It's Karva Chauth.

1414
01:55:24,476 --> 01:55:26,463
I have my husband's picture
with me, although he's away.

1415
01:55:26,543 --> 01:55:29,406
I'll pay my respects to him.
Let's go.

1416
01:55:30,153 --> 01:55:31,863
Great is Indian culture!

1417
01:55:32,353 --> 01:55:34,148
lf not man, his picture
will do!

1418
01:55:44,361 --> 01:55:47,475
Look at that, sister!
- What is it?

1419
01:55:48,420 --> 01:55:49,463
There! Right in the front!

1420
01:55:51,341 --> 01:55:52,683
Why don't you wear
your glasses?

1421
01:55:54,241 --> 01:55:55,552
What is it?

1422
01:55:55,767 --> 01:55:58,244
There's a girl with Amit's
picture in her hand.

1423
01:56:07,140 --> 01:56:12,151
I think it's the same girl
Amit's in love with.

1424
01:56:13,594 --> 01:56:16,955
I suspect Amit has
married her on the sly.

1425
01:56:17,386 --> 01:56:18,538
That's possible!

1426
01:56:18,858 --> 01:56:21,951
Or what would the wretch be
doing here on this day?

1427
01:56:22,761 --> 01:56:25,585
Let's go! I'll teach her
a lesson today!

1428
01:56:36,334 --> 01:56:37,549
Mother!

1429
01:56:38,710 --> 01:56:42,616
Madhuri! It's you?!

1430
01:56:45,239 --> 01:56:48,301
When did you come to Bombay?
You didn't even inform me!

1431
01:56:49,059 --> 01:56:51,086
How have you been?
Where are you staying?

1432
01:56:51,430 --> 01:56:56,003
It's your blessing that has
me happy wherever I am.

1433
01:56:57,199 --> 01:57:00,984
This is my daughter-in-law,
Saraswati.

1434
01:57:01,426 --> 01:57:04,049
Although my son has
not accepted her...

1435
01:57:04,559 --> 01:57:06,837
she still revers her husband
on this day!

1436
01:57:07,387 --> 01:57:10,203
This is my sister, Saraswati.

1437
01:57:10,567 --> 01:57:11,804
Hello, aunty.
- Bless you.

1438
01:57:11,884 --> 01:57:15,639
Am I not unfortunate to
have such a useless son!

1439
01:57:16,219 --> 01:57:17,842
He has forsaken a beautiful
wife like you...

1440
01:57:18,175 --> 01:57:20,259
and is lusting after
the city-bred girls!

1441
01:57:22,741 --> 01:57:28,169
It's true. Although it's shameful,
it's necessary to inform you.

1442
01:57:28,507 --> 01:57:31,476
Amit is caught in the clutches
of a secretary in his office.

1443
01:57:32,013 --> 01:57:34,006
While you are doing your
duty as a wife...

1444
01:57:34,086 --> 01:57:37,276
that man is enticed
by a shameless wretch!

1445
01:57:37,575 --> 01:57:39,418
This is the sign of
impending doom!

1446
01:57:40,129 --> 01:57:41,348
No, Saraswati!

1447
01:57:41,941 --> 01:57:45,192
Now that we've found her,
we will not let that happen!

1448
01:57:46,080 --> 01:57:48,587
Come home with me, Madhuri.

1449
01:57:48,950 --> 01:57:52,279
Let's take a decision
on this day!

1450
01:57:52,359 --> 01:57:55,680
I beg of you! Save Amit
from this destruction!

1451
01:57:55,760 --> 01:57:59,556
Please don't worry, Mother.

1452
01:57:59,780 --> 01:58:01,610
Everything is okay, 
by the grace of God.

1453
01:58:05,437 --> 01:58:08,499
The woman who has enticed
your son in her trap...

1454
01:58:09,229 --> 01:58:12,220
is none other than me.

1455
01:58:14,288 --> 01:58:19,989
You? Are you Amit's private
secretary, Malti Chaudhary?

1456
01:58:20,288 --> 01:58:24,625
Yes. I'm Madhuri...
and also Malti.

1457
01:58:25,004 --> 01:58:26,992
How did you work
this miracle?

1458
01:58:28,259 --> 01:58:31,451
It is the result of a woman's
sincerity and dedication.

1459
01:58:32,498 --> 01:58:35,488
I had made up my mind, that
should I have the strength...

1460
01:58:35,568 --> 01:58:38,146
and should my marriage
be sacred...

1461
01:58:38,226 --> 01:58:40,486
my husband would himself
come back to me.

1462
01:58:41,762 --> 01:58:43,662
And that is what
has happened.

1463
01:58:44,252 --> 01:58:48,043
I always knew that you and
your husband dote on me.

1464
01:58:48,677 --> 01:58:53,868
But I was scared whether
my husband would accept me.

1465
01:58:54,642 --> 01:58:57,263
But I've had enough
of this now.

1466
01:58:57,703 --> 01:59:00,316
Please take me to my house.
- No, my dear.

1467
01:59:00,774 --> 01:59:06,167
The game isn't over as yet.
Our husbands are yet to be punished.

1468
01:59:07,037 --> 01:59:09,501
My husband has played
practical jokes all his life.

1469
01:59:09,950 --> 01:59:13,373
In fact, he reduced our
lives to a cheap joke.

1470
01:59:14,086 --> 01:59:20,403
And my son kept looking for
wisdom, through his glasses.

1471
01:59:20,825 --> 01:59:23,104
Be patient, Madhuri.

1472
01:59:23,438 --> 01:59:28,215
Let us both teach our
husbands a lesson!

1473
01:59:28,919 --> 01:59:31,329
Let's shake hands on that,
daughter-in-law! Go on!

1474
02:00:08,075 --> 02:00:13,098
Is the cold war between
father and son still on?

1475
02:00:13,851 --> 02:00:16,635
Must you show how silly you
are, the moment you arrive?

1476
02:00:16,715 --> 02:00:20,730
Do I? You're the sensible ones!
You will learn a lesson now!

1477
02:00:20,975 --> 02:00:22,463
What kind of a wife are you?

1478
02:00:23,203 --> 02:00:25,179
You're always rubbing salt
in my wounds!

1479
02:00:25,435 --> 02:00:31,061
You deserved to be thrown in a sea
of salt for what you've done!

1480
02:00:39,616 --> 02:00:40,616
Who's that?

1481
02:00:40,847 --> 02:00:45,242
This is his private secretary
Miss Malti Chaudhary.

1482
02:00:45,424 --> 02:00:47,457
Malti Chaudhary?!

1483
02:00:47,694 --> 02:00:52,475
So you are the wretch who's
trying to rape my son!

1484
02:00:54,460 --> 02:00:56,677
How's Amit keeping now?

1485
02:00:56,853 --> 02:01:00,672
Don't you know?
He died of a heart-failure!

1486
02:01:00,752 --> 02:01:03,153
God-forbid! What nonsense!

1487
02:01:03,992 --> 02:01:07,419
Let me speak to her...
- No! I won't!

1488
02:01:07,661 --> 02:01:09,056
Go away!

1489
02:01:10,485 --> 02:01:13,234
Haven't you disconnected
as yet, you wretch!

1490
02:01:15,372 --> 02:01:18,369
How can you say that,
father-in-law?

1491
02:01:18,848 --> 02:01:21,768
I'm still trying
to connect...

1492
02:01:21,848 --> 02:01:24,460
and you're talking of
disconnecting !

1493
02:01:25,771 --> 02:01:28,159
Don't you dare call me
father-in-law !

1494
02:01:28,797 --> 02:01:31,990
Bloody sinner!
Bloody lady bandit!

1495
02:01:32,070 --> 02:01:35,351
Listen carefully to me!

1496
02:01:35,855 --> 02:01:38,341
Should you even dare
to look at my son...

1497
02:01:39,035 --> 02:01:42,672
I'll use hired goons to
hack you to pieces!

1498
02:01:42,894 --> 02:01:46,753
You're a liar,
father-in-law!

1499
02:01:47,685 --> 02:01:49,811
You call me father-in-law
again! What do you mean?

1500
02:01:49,891 --> 02:01:52,990
Didn't you lie that
Amit is dead?

1501
02:01:54,099 --> 02:01:56,399
I'm alive, darling!

1502
02:01:56,479 --> 02:01:59,239
Our love is alive, too!
No one can separate us!

1503
02:01:59,607 --> 02:02:01,451
Who's that speaking
on the line?

1504
02:02:01,531 --> 02:02:03,390
Can't you hear me speaking
to the wretched woman?

1505
02:02:03,856 --> 02:02:08,233
You witch! Sorceress!
Bloody bandit!

1506
02:02:08,730 --> 02:02:12,261
Amit is as good as
dead for you!

1507
02:02:14,758 --> 02:02:17,501
This is a cross-connection!
Just hang up!

1508
02:02:18,424 --> 02:02:21,610
So what were you saying,
you cursed woman?

1509
02:02:22,359 --> 02:02:26,806
All I want to tell you,
father-in-law...

1510
02:02:26,886 --> 02:02:28,828
is the truth that
love is blind!

1511
02:02:28,908 --> 02:02:32,017
You're right!
- Right, my foot!

1512
02:02:32,771 --> 02:02:37,179
Aren't you ashamed
to eavesdrop on us?

1513
02:02:37,527 --> 02:02:41,359
So what did you say?
That love is blind, eh?

1514
02:02:41,788 --> 02:02:44,333
That could be the case.
But I'm not blind!

1515
02:02:44,718 --> 02:02:48,238
If a whore dares
eye my son...

1516
02:02:48,544 --> 02:02:50,647
I'll have her eyes pulled
out of the sockets!

1517
02:02:52,169 --> 02:02:54,861
Why must you take
the trouble?

1518
02:02:55,099 --> 02:02:58,462
If my love is true...

1519
02:02:58,542 --> 02:03:04,283
I will send my eyes to you
on a platter!

1520
02:03:04,363 --> 02:03:05,831
Very well. Have them
sent by this evening.

1521
02:03:05,911 --> 02:03:10,714
Don't do that! It will
plunge my world in darkness!

1522
02:03:12,324 --> 02:03:13,943
Now listen, you cursed woman!

1523
02:03:14,023 --> 02:03:17,317
We will very soon bring our
daughter-in-law home...

1524
02:03:17,620 --> 02:03:19,763
and have her compete with you
in a beauty-contest!

1525
02:03:19,987 --> 02:03:21,561
Just you wait!

1526
02:03:23,699 --> 02:03:27,905
I can't wait.
Bring the village belle here.

1527
02:03:27,985 --> 02:03:33,315
If I don't rob her
of her marital status...

1528
02:03:33,395 --> 02:03:36,789
I will never boast again!

1529
02:03:43,081 --> 02:03:44,814
Either of us lives now!

1530
02:03:54,597 --> 02:03:56,752
Are you asleep or awake?

1531
02:03:57,894 --> 02:04:00,260
I don't know whether
I'm asleep or awake!

1532
02:04:00,340 --> 02:04:02,616
Whether I'm alive or dead!

1533
02:04:05,562 --> 02:04:11,324
I understand it, Amit.
I understand it all.

1534
02:04:13,135 --> 02:04:15,105
Your father will never
accept me.

1535
02:04:16,364 --> 02:04:17,351
Isn't that what you're
trying to say?

1536
02:04:17,650 --> 02:04:19,743
Give me one last chance, Malti!

1537
02:04:19,823 --> 02:04:22,752
I'll somehow try and
bring my father around!

1538
02:04:23,121 --> 02:04:25,867
But you love me, don't you?

1539
02:04:27,582 --> 02:04:30,678
Yes, I do. I love you more
than I love my life.

1540
02:04:31,048 --> 02:04:34,752
Will you still love me, even
if I'm not in a position...

1541
02:04:35,174 --> 02:04:36,679
to pay your parents?

1542
02:04:41,279 --> 02:04:45,071
You don't need to ask.
- That's it then!

1543
02:04:45,151 --> 02:04:48,638
Let's have a registered
marriage in court!

1544
02:04:48,718 --> 02:04:50,896
My Mom will stand witness.

1545
02:04:51,072 --> 02:04:54,373
I'll give your parents
a written undertaking...

1546
02:04:54,453 --> 02:04:57,014
that they can have half
my salary...

1547
02:04:57,094 --> 02:04:59,412
till such time as their
demand of dowry is met!

1548
02:04:59,791 --> 02:05:02,396
Isn't that okay?
- Okay.

1549
02:05:03,019 --> 02:05:04,842
No power on earth
can stop us now!

1550
02:05:04,922 --> 02:05:07,154
Not your parents...
Not my cruel father!

1551
02:05:07,453 --> 02:05:10,292
Let's meet at the Registrar's office
at 4 p.m. the day after, then. Okay?

1552
02:05:10,735 --> 02:05:12,246
You will come there,
won't you?

1553
02:05:17,636 --> 02:05:18,714
But remember.

1554
02:05:19,193 --> 02:05:22,049
This will be the last
scene of our love-story.

1555
02:05:28,410 --> 02:05:29,721
Listen...

1556
02:05:30,081 --> 02:05:31,379
We are doomed!

1557
02:05:32,625 --> 02:05:34,337
What are you doing here?

1558
02:05:34,525 --> 02:05:37,346
Can't you see me
reading the newspapers?

1559
02:05:37,568 --> 02:05:39,709
You can read the news
tomorrow...

1560
02:05:40,213 --> 02:05:43,109
when our son figures
in the headlines!

1561
02:05:43,440 --> 02:05:46,307
Why? Is he being given
a national award?

1562
02:05:46,771 --> 02:05:50,339
He's my son, after all!
- Your son? Big deal!

1563
02:05:50,419 --> 02:05:53,357
Let's hurry up... Amit is
about to play courtesan.

1564
02:05:53,573 --> 02:05:59,925
What?! Courtesan?
Has he had a sex-change?

1565
02:06:00,264 --> 02:06:03,667
He's going to commit suicide
the way the courtesan did!

1566
02:06:03,884 --> 02:06:06,390
He's burying himself alive!

1567
02:06:06,996 --> 02:06:08,378
He dares!

1568
02:06:32,231 --> 02:06:34,786
What are you up to, my son?

1569
02:06:35,154 --> 02:06:38,012
I'm sacrificing myself
in the name of love!

1570
02:06:38,453 --> 02:06:41,989
You are about to undertake
a great deed, my son!

1571
02:06:42,475 --> 02:06:44,189
It will immortalise
our family name!

1572
02:06:44,726 --> 02:06:49,416
But to bury yourself in sand
and cement is a cheap way.

1573
02:06:49,614 --> 02:06:51,158
You should have thought
of a better way.

1574
02:06:51,238 --> 02:06:54,598
No! This is how I will die!

1575
02:06:55,125 --> 02:06:57,310
Those last bricks...

1576
02:06:57,466 --> 02:06:59,399
will cement my death,
the moment I signal it!

1577
02:06:59,673 --> 02:07:02,985
The path of my life
will be shut forever!

1578
02:07:03,959 --> 02:07:07,862
My darling son!
Deign to tell me...

1579
02:07:07,942 --> 02:07:12,328
whom are you dying for?
- For Malti!

1580
02:07:15,431 --> 02:07:18,843
Scoundrel! I must place
the last brick then!

1581
02:07:18,923 --> 02:07:22,238
You will be hanged for that!
- I'll bribe my way out!

1582
02:07:22,527 --> 02:07:25,068
Listen!
Don't kill our son!

1583
02:07:25,148 --> 02:07:29,797
I've had every experience in life
except that of murder.

1584
02:07:30,367 --> 02:07:32,190
Let me satisfy myself today.

1585
02:07:35,196 --> 02:07:37,998
Let's prepare to leave
for the crematorium!

1586
02:07:44,803 --> 02:07:46,288
What a bloody father!

1587
02:07:53,705 --> 02:07:57,907
That's 200 grams of gold, okay?

1588
02:07:57,987 --> 02:08:00,068
Okay, aunty.
I get it!

1589
02:08:00,148 --> 02:08:02,116
Go on! He's coming
this way!

1590
02:08:03,175 --> 02:08:05,803
He'll end his life,
he says! Big deal!

1591
02:08:06,222 --> 02:08:10,208
But I'm no mean father...
I'm a dictator myself!

1592
02:08:11,090 --> 02:08:13,940
What's this?
Gold?

1593
02:08:14,591 --> 02:08:18,973
Come and take a look!
We have stolen gold in our house!

1594
02:08:23,029 --> 02:08:27,041
That's not stolen gold,
Mister!

1595
02:08:27,631 --> 02:08:29,636
It's my hard-earned
savings!

1596
02:08:29,716 --> 02:08:32,284
What nonsense are you talking?

1597
02:08:32,925 --> 02:08:37,483
It's not nonsense...
I'm telling you something!

1598
02:08:40,200 --> 02:08:41,413
Okay. Go on. 

1599
02:08:41,493 --> 02:08:45,531
Take a good look, Mr Chaudhary!

1600
02:08:45,701 --> 02:08:50,362
Or show it to a jeweller!
The gold is for real!

1601
02:08:51,234 --> 02:08:53,780
I know that. I'm not blind.
But what is it for?

1602
02:08:58,343 --> 02:09:01,265
You had once asked for
200 grams of gold...

1603
02:09:01,345 --> 02:09:03,911
to accept my sister as
your daughter-in-law.

1604
02:09:04,093 --> 02:09:05,623
There is the 200 grams!

1605
02:09:05,703 --> 02:09:09,029
I've kept my promise.
You must honour your word now.

1606
02:09:09,109 --> 02:09:12,133
Or I'll assume that you are
a two-tongued fraud!

1607
02:09:18,461 --> 02:09:21,641
I wish you had landed
this slap on me...

1608
02:09:22,058 --> 02:09:23,807
when I joked
about the gold.

1609
02:09:25,623 --> 02:09:29,284
You have slapped me repeatedly
by showing me this gold today!

1610
02:09:30,529 --> 02:09:32,317
I had only joked
with you!

1611
02:09:33,581 --> 02:09:37,181
And my son Amit,
who hates village folks...

1612
02:09:37,777 --> 02:09:39,677
cashed in on my jokes.

1613
02:09:40,619 --> 02:09:43,317
I want nothing of this!
I already have it all!

1614
02:09:43,979 --> 02:09:45,048
Come with me...

1615
02:09:52,328 --> 02:09:57,368
Take a look at the
jewellery and money!

1616
02:09:59,850 --> 02:10:02,999
I'm perhaps the only man in
these times of robberies...

1617
02:10:03,079 --> 02:10:05,322
who keeps no less than
half a million in cash!

1618
02:10:06,201 --> 02:10:09,004
Who does it all belong to?
To my son, of course.

1619
02:10:09,404 --> 02:10:11,304
And to my daughter-in-law.

1620
02:10:17,392 --> 02:10:21,490
My real treasure and the
wealth of this family...

1621
02:10:23,066 --> 02:10:29,135
is peace and love and
my daughter-in-law.

1622
02:10:29,968 --> 02:10:31,742
I want nothing but
my daughter-in-law!

1623
02:10:31,822 --> 02:10:34,052
Listen! We are doomed!

1624
02:10:34,285 --> 02:10:37,830
There's terrible news
from Madhuri!

1625
02:10:37,910 --> 02:10:42,167
May I read it?
- Why must you ask! Go on!

1626
02:10:42,247 --> 02:10:44,976
My greetings to those who
consider women an object...

1627
02:10:45,056 --> 02:10:47,507
of pleasure and
a mere commodity.

1628
02:10:49,567 --> 02:10:51,524
I'm sending you
200 grams of gold...

1629
02:10:51,604 --> 02:10:54,313
which I want you all to lick
to your heart's satisfaction!

1630
02:10:55,804 --> 02:10:59,379
I'm a modern woman, who is
standing on her own two feet.

1631
02:10:59,657 --> 02:11:01,424
I am taking my
own decisions.

1632
02:11:01,504 --> 02:11:05,904
And I have decided
to dispatch to hell...

1633
02:11:06,142 --> 02:11:09,013
my useless husband and
my greedy father-in-law!

1634
02:11:09,264 --> 02:11:11,974
I'm getting married again,
without a divorce.

1635
02:11:12,054 --> 02:11:13,707
The fortunate Madhuri!

1636
02:11:13,909 --> 02:11:18,628
No! This cannot be!
I won't let that happen!

1637
02:11:18,976 --> 02:11:21,501
You mustn't let that
happen, Shreekant!

1638
02:11:21,809 --> 02:11:25,064
It would kill me!
I wouldn't live anymore!

1639
02:11:25,275 --> 02:11:28,618
I beg of you, Shreekant!
I beg at your feet!

1640
02:11:29,348 --> 02:11:33,156
You are making a sinner
out of me, sir!

1641
02:11:33,683 --> 02:11:37,334
It is I who has sinned. To play
such jokes is also a sin.

1642
02:11:38,013 --> 02:11:39,254
I am the sinner.

1643
02:11:39,974 --> 02:11:44,592
But ask your sister not
to punish me like this.

1644
02:11:45,999 --> 02:11:48,972
Only you can help me now.

1645
02:11:50,239 --> 02:11:52,640
I swear by God...

1646
02:11:53,107 --> 02:11:55,413
I'll never play
such a joke again!

1647
02:11:56,363 --> 02:12:00,357
Please forgive me, sir!
I've hurt your feelings!

1648
02:12:00,437 --> 02:12:02,578
I can't bear to see
your plight anymore!

1649
02:12:03,754 --> 02:12:06,623
You will light the
Diwali lamps tomorrow...

1650
02:12:06,703 --> 02:12:09,384
only after my sister
arrives in this house!

1651
02:12:09,842 --> 02:12:12,772
That is a solemn promise
I make to you!

1652
02:12:15,393 --> 02:12:16,774
Let's embrace!

1653
02:13:15,263 --> 02:13:17,727
Malti will surely arrive.
Don't worry.

1654
02:13:18,064 --> 02:13:20,168
She must be getting ready
or even feeling shy.

1655
02:13:20,843 --> 02:13:23,428
Although this is a
registered marriage,...

1656
02:13:23,974 --> 02:13:26,764
she can't forget
our customs.

1657
02:13:26,844 --> 02:13:29,143
I hope we don't miss the
date in the process!

1658
02:13:29,223 --> 02:13:31,036
That's what I'm really
worried about.

1659
02:13:31,939 --> 02:13:33,852
I have a feeling that she
will surely turn up.

1660
02:13:34,566 --> 02:13:36,468
Maybe she's gone to
buy a garland.

1661
02:13:36,548 --> 02:13:39,085
I told her that I hate
this hackneyed customs.

1662
02:13:39,165 --> 02:13:40,635
If I had to adhere to
these customs...

1663
02:13:40,715 --> 02:13:42,732
why'd I get married again
in this manner?

1664
02:13:43,188 --> 02:13:47,157
No one knows that you
are already married!

1665
02:13:47,740 --> 02:13:49,387
Speak softly, Mom! 
What are you doing?!

1666
02:14:04,006 --> 02:14:06,944
My left-eye is
fluttering, Mom!

1667
02:14:07,330 --> 02:14:09,505
I suspect we have a
calamity on hand!

1668
02:14:09,759 --> 02:14:12,740
You shouldn't utter such
inauspicious words, my son.

1669
02:14:13,972 --> 02:14:15,523
There she is!

1670
02:14:43,277 --> 02:14:46,885
What's that, Malti? You have
matrimonial vermillion in your hair?!

1671
02:14:47,149 --> 02:14:48,707
It's I who must apply
the vermillion on you!

1672
02:14:49,261 --> 02:14:52,311
I see! This is Malti then!

1673
02:14:53,402 --> 02:14:57,392
Is it your custom to apply
vermillion before marriage?

1674
02:14:57,864 --> 02:15:00,335
What's all that about?

1675
02:15:00,685 --> 02:15:04,607
It's vermillion. The marital
status of a woman!

1676
02:15:05,474 --> 02:15:09,039
Stop joking, Malti!

1677
02:15:09,535 --> 02:15:11,391
You're going to give me
a heart-attack!

1678
02:15:11,471 --> 02:15:13,319
You should have had
a heart-attack...

1679
02:15:13,844 --> 02:15:16,224
the day you walked out on
an innocent village girl...

1680
02:15:16,596 --> 02:15:19,662
trembling and crying, even
after you had married her!

1681
02:15:20,115 --> 02:15:23,863
Had you a heart, you'd have
suffered an attack the day...

1682
02:15:24,273 --> 02:15:26,372
you feigned love for me,...

1683
02:15:26,743 --> 02:15:28,705
without telling me that
you're a married man!

1684
02:15:28,785 --> 02:15:34,908
She knows everything, Amit!
What happens now?

1685
02:15:35,221 --> 02:15:36,889
Keep quiet, mother.

1686
02:15:39,519 --> 02:15:41,651
How can you do this, Mother?

1687
02:15:42,152 --> 02:15:44,010
Even as your first daughter-
in-law still lives...

1688
02:15:44,090 --> 02:15:46,731
how can you stand witness in
your son's second marriage?

1689
02:15:47,931 --> 02:15:49,242
I couldn't help it!

1690
02:15:49,941 --> 02:15:52,504
My love for my son
has blinded me!

1691
02:15:56,220 --> 02:15:59,440
You have put on act with me;
and so did I with you.

1692
02:16:00,172 --> 02:16:03,034
You are a married man;
and I'm a married woman.

1693
02:16:03,616 --> 02:16:05,192
When you had the right
to fall in love,...

1694
02:16:05,272 --> 02:16:08,912
inspite of being married,
I have the same right, too!

1695
02:16:09,729 --> 02:16:12,757
She's right, Amit.
- Quiet!

1696
02:16:14,813 --> 02:16:19,077
Despite all this, I still
have a lot of respect for you.

1697
02:16:19,582 --> 02:16:22,570
Bless me then that my
return to my husband...

1698
02:16:22,828 --> 02:16:24,981
be auspicious and
God-blessed.

1699
02:16:26,400 --> 02:16:28,672
May you be happy.

1700
02:16:35,412 --> 02:16:38,192
There's only one
way out now, son.

1701
02:16:38,889 --> 02:16:41,857
Let's bring Madhuri home
on this day of Diwali.

1702
02:16:42,589 --> 02:16:44,915
The second wife has
fled with her husband.

1703
02:16:45,514 --> 02:16:47,678
We only have the first
daughter-in-law now.

1704
02:16:48,049 --> 02:16:50,702
There's a great awakening
among women these days.

1705
02:16:51,155 --> 02:16:53,337
I hope the your
first wife...

1706
02:16:53,724 --> 02:16:55,647
doesn't marry
someone else, too!

1707
02:17:08,643 --> 02:17:11,258
Why are you laughing?
- I was reminded of something!

1708
02:17:12,094 --> 02:17:16,047
Isn't this how you paced up
and down when Amit was born?

1709
02:17:16,663 --> 02:17:20,353
What else could I do?
I was expecting my son then.

1710
02:17:21,229 --> 02:17:24,266
And I'm expecting
my daughter-in-law now.

1711
02:17:24,658 --> 02:17:26,822
Why hasn't she arrived?
- You have changed for good.

1712
02:17:27,133 --> 02:17:29,104
But your son is still as
fickle-minded as ever.

1713
02:17:29,454 --> 02:17:32,567
What if he refuses
to accept Malti...

1714
02:17:32,647 --> 02:17:34,690
I'm not a fool either!

1715
02:17:34,847 --> 02:17:36,873
Look at these documents!

1716
02:17:37,227 --> 02:17:39,771
I have bequeathed all my
property and wealth...

1717
02:17:39,851 --> 02:17:42,075
to the daughter-in-law!

1718
02:17:42,301 --> 02:17:44,765
Let me see how he
refuses to accept her!

1719
02:17:50,957 --> 02:17:52,334
Daughter-in-law!

1720
02:17:53,064 --> 02:17:54,499
Come along...

1721
02:18:13,606 --> 02:18:16,875
We have the Goddess here
in person this auspicious day.

1722
02:18:17,928 --> 02:18:21,080
Do come in, daughter-in-law
and bless this house.

1723
02:18:23,253 --> 02:18:24,801
Come in, dear.

1724
02:18:30,291 --> 02:18:33,720
No! I have already sinned!
Do not commit me to anymore sins!

1725
02:18:35,095 --> 02:18:37,556
We have all made some
mistake or the other.

1726
02:18:38,230 --> 02:18:40,365
But God has forgiven us
and made you return to us.

1727
02:18:40,963 --> 02:18:45,687
Take care of your home now.
- Isn't her husband at home?

1728
02:18:46,093 --> 02:18:47,394
Don't even utter his name!

1729
02:18:49,022 --> 02:18:51,108
I don't want to hide
anything from you, dear.

1730
02:18:51,622 --> 02:18:53,359
Amit has really heaped
humiliation on me.

1731
02:18:53,825 --> 02:18:56,036
He has ruined the
family's reputation.

1732
02:18:57,200 --> 02:18:58,522
But don't you worry!

1733
02:18:59,051 --> 02:19:00,911
If he still does not
come to his senses...

1734
02:19:00,991 --> 02:19:02,337
I will throw him
out of the house.

1735
02:19:02,436 --> 02:19:04,691
Look; I have bequeathed
everything to you.

1736
02:19:04,990 --> 02:19:06,776
All my wealth and estate!

1737
02:19:06,856 --> 02:19:10,875
Please don't say that...
that can never happen!

1738
02:19:11,473 --> 02:19:16,272
Because I'm Madhuri
and Malti, too!

1739
02:19:16,352 --> 02:19:18,389
What?!
- That's right!

1740
02:19:18,794 --> 02:19:20,613
What she says is true.

1741
02:19:21,267 --> 02:19:23,643
When our son rejected her...

1742
02:19:24,021 --> 02:19:27,003
she had to strive and stand
on her own two feet.

1743
02:19:27,733 --> 02:19:29,909
She found a job
in Amit's office...

1744
02:19:30,451 --> 02:19:32,633
and enticed him
as Malti.

1745
02:19:34,911 --> 02:19:39,495
I had to turn Malti in order
to win back my husband.

1746
02:19:39,846 --> 02:19:46,996
Fantastic! You are the
epitome of all virtue!

1747
02:19:48,196 --> 02:19:50,878
Does the ass know
the truth yet?

1748
02:19:50,958 --> 02:19:54,304
Who's that?
- The ass! Amit!

1749
02:19:54,855 --> 02:19:55,929
No. He doesn't.

1750
02:19:56,403 --> 02:19:58,621
Fantastic! This is going to be fun!

1751
02:19:58,981 --> 02:20:01,300
I have now started believing
in your God, too!

1752
02:20:02,087 --> 02:20:05,093
He will come back, all right.
Where would he go anyway?

1753
02:20:05,720 --> 02:20:07,719
Take daughter-in-law
upstairs, Saraswati.

1754
02:20:09,020 --> 02:20:11,594
I'll deal with the ass!

1755
02:20:18,188 --> 02:20:22,841
All my dreams are
fulfilled today, Shreekant.

1756
02:20:22,921 --> 02:20:24,919
Of course. You had to
realise your dreams.

1757
02:20:25,146 --> 02:20:26,581
As for Amit...

1758
02:20:27,345 --> 02:20:30,946
let him return. And see
how I deal with him!

1759
02:20:56,670 --> 02:20:59,330
When have I turned Pop
from Dad ?

1760
02:21:00,053 --> 02:21:04,289
Since I've turned
what I am.

1761
02:21:04,715 --> 02:21:07,713
Are you drunk?
- What else could I do?

1762
02:21:08,119 --> 02:21:11,184
My father has been drinking
to my grief, all my life.

1763
02:21:11,551 --> 02:21:14,136
To drown my sorrows then,
I had some liquor today.

1764
02:21:14,462 --> 02:21:18,807
I haven't had much...
it's only 10 or 12 drinks.

1765
02:21:19,449 --> 02:21:20,580
Listen, son...

1766
02:21:22,977 --> 02:21:26,720
There's no son and father
anymore. It's all over!

1767
02:21:27,614 --> 02:21:30,821
Throw that cursed bottle away.
And look who's here.

1768
02:21:31,186 --> 02:21:33,500
Your brother-in-law, Shreekant.
- Greetings, brother-in-law!

1769
02:21:33,580 --> 02:21:35,599
Damn the brother-in-law!

1770
02:21:36,245 --> 02:21:41,128
I'll tell you today what you'd
have, if not the Himalayas!

1771
02:21:41,338 --> 02:21:43,846
You'd have a great wall
in my father instead!

1772
02:21:44,066 --> 02:21:47,420
Who'd destroy the world with
his misplaced ideals!

1773
02:21:47,500 --> 02:21:50,027
And they'd be forced to
like bitter-gourd!

1774
02:21:50,107 --> 02:21:52,910
What are you saying, Amit?!

1775
02:21:53,672 --> 02:21:55,466
We wanted to give you
a piece of good news.

1776
02:21:55,546 --> 02:21:58,916
What good news?
- You'll get a slap...

1777
02:22:00,677 --> 02:22:03,059
You are our only son.

1778
02:22:03,499 --> 02:22:05,478
In your happiness lies
our own happiness, too.

1779
02:22:05,918 --> 02:22:08,655
We will forget your wife
Madhuri, as you have.

1780
02:22:08,735 --> 02:22:12,226
We will also get you
married to your lover, Malti.

1781
02:22:12,306 --> 02:22:15,104
Yes! Let's forget everything
else, except Malti!

1782
02:22:20,064 --> 02:22:23,255
She feigned love for me!

1783
02:22:24,032 --> 02:22:27,204
She has cheated me!

1784
02:22:27,639 --> 02:22:29,903
I wouldn't want to set my
eyes on her ever again!

1785
02:22:30,357 --> 02:22:33,720
She has betrayed me!

1786
02:22:34,184 --> 02:22:36,907
We want to forget just
what you are trying to.

1787
02:22:37,070 --> 02:22:41,990
We can even bring Madhuri
home, should you be willing.

1788
02:22:43,080 --> 02:22:49,860
What joke is this between
Madhuri and Malti?!

1789
02:22:50,937 --> 02:22:52,694
I want neither!

1790
02:22:52,774 --> 02:22:55,317
Neither the village-belle
nor the city-bred!

1791
02:22:55,397 --> 02:22:57,793
I will remain a bachelor
all my life.

1792
02:22:57,873 --> 02:23:02,717
And I will show everyone
how you have ruined my life!

1793
02:23:02,797 --> 02:23:05,829
You have! A wicked
father has!

1794
02:23:05,909 --> 02:23:11,589
Who has killed and mauled
his only son!

1795
02:23:11,840 --> 02:23:13,125
Don't worry!

1796
02:23:13,503 --> 02:23:16,180
Everything will be fine,
the moment he goes upstairs.

1797
02:23:28,095 --> 02:23:30,726
You?! What the hell
are you doing here?

1798
02:23:34,356 --> 02:23:39,591
Forgive me.
I had no other choice.

1799
02:23:42,373 --> 02:23:44,958
You scheming bitch!

1800
02:23:45,181 --> 02:23:47,174
You first pretended to
fall in love with me!

1801
02:23:47,254 --> 02:23:49,735
And you've gotten into my house now!
Get the hell out of here!

1802
02:23:49,967 --> 02:23:52,730
Get out, I say!

1803
02:23:52,810 --> 02:23:56,170
I will end the
drama you've begun!

1804
02:23:58,431 --> 02:23:59,933
Get out!

1805
02:24:00,692 --> 02:24:02,847
Not a word from you!

1806
02:24:04,343 --> 02:24:05,741
Listen to me...
- Come on!

1807
02:24:16,713 --> 02:24:17,942
Let's go!

1808
02:24:27,199 --> 02:24:30,218
What's that?
- The marriage altar.

1809
02:24:31,493 --> 02:24:34,293
What do you mean?
- I'll explain.

1810
02:24:35,179 --> 02:24:38,065
Ladies and gentlemen...

1811
02:24:38,420 --> 02:24:39,647
Hold it, you idiot!

1812
02:24:39,851 --> 02:24:43,875
How dare you address them
without our presence?

1813
02:24:45,022 --> 02:24:46,700
Get on with your speech!

1814
02:24:47,751 --> 02:24:49,618
Ladies and gentlemen...

1815
02:24:50,338 --> 02:24:53,587
you mustn't have heard or
seen a marriage of this kind.

1816
02:24:54,368 --> 02:24:58,326
A man is marrying his wife
for the second time today.

1817
02:24:58,792 --> 02:24:59,883
What does that mean?

1818
02:24:59,963 --> 02:25:04,202
Just as I had humiliated
my wife in public...

1819
02:25:04,282 --> 02:25:06,658
at the wedding-altar
one day...

1820
02:25:07,274 --> 02:25:14,335
I now apologise to my wife
in your presence with folded hands.

1821
02:25:14,415 --> 02:25:16,609
What's that you're doing?

1822
02:25:16,827 --> 02:25:18,899
I married Madhuri
during the days...

1823
02:25:20,197 --> 02:25:22,132
when I was blinded by the
glasses of stupidity.

1824
02:25:22,458 --> 02:25:25,827
My father cast a shadow
in one of the lens!

1825
02:25:27,331 --> 02:25:30,000
It did take time.
But I realised the truth.

1826
02:25:31,009 --> 02:25:33,868
I was the only filth
around my rose-like wife.

1827
02:25:34,194 --> 02:25:37,458
And also...
- Your father!

1828
02:25:37,643 --> 02:25:39,408
Before this sacred fire,...

1829
02:25:40,538 --> 02:25:42,486
around which we have
taken the vows...

1830
02:25:43,363 --> 02:25:48,149
I choose Madhuri as my
companion till eternity!

1831
02:25:49,566 --> 02:25:53,418
Please forgive me, Madhuri.

1832
02:25:53,779 --> 02:25:57,500
Don't say that!
But how did you...

1833
02:25:58,212 --> 02:26:01,362
Don't be angry, my dear.

1834
02:26:01,538 --> 02:26:03,685
I couldn't see him upset.

1835
02:26:03,993 --> 02:26:06,809
And so I told him
the whole truth.

1836
02:26:07,346 --> 02:26:08,921
Forgive him, dear.

1837
02:26:09,348 --> 02:26:14,727
I knew the bitter-gourd would
drill some sense into him!

1838
02:26:15,624 --> 02:26:19,206
I'll answer you today, Shreekant.
Had it not been for the Himalayas...

1839
02:26:19,526 --> 02:26:20,508
What would we have then?

1840
02:26:21,078 --> 02:26:23,005
We'd have the daughter-in-law!
